  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study aims to investigate prospectively and systematically the direct and&#xD;
      indirect complications occurring within 30 days after guided-bronchoscopy and/or&#xD;
      endosonography. The results of the study should reliably help clarify further incidence,&#xD;
      pattern, risk factors, and outcomes for both immediate and late complications associated with&#xD;
      these key diagnostic procedures.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
